---
title: Quick Southern Cheesy Pork Quesadillas with Cucumber Salsa & Sour Cream
description: Juicy Southern-spiced pork, sour cream and melted Cheddar cheese; it’s hard to resist these incredibly delicious quesadillas. Plus, it takes less than 30 minutes to have this fun feast on your dinner table!
